    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/caf92859355ca0483e27643f4cce5058.poster.avif?t=1723083184\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/caf92859355ca0483e27643f4cce5058.webm?t=1723083184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/caf92859355ca0483e27643f4cce5058.mp4?t=1723083184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dungeon Digger</strong> 是一款关于勇敢的矮人寻找传说中宝藏的roguelike游戏。下降到地下王国的最深层，开采越来越有价值的矿物，以制造优质装备。与危险的蜘蛛、石像、地下蠕虫和幽灵战斗，成为这些黑暗洞穴的英雄!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/60ee0dc55af0b898ac807695e2440f3b.poster.avif?t=1723083184\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/60ee0dc55af0b898ac807695e2440f3b.webm?t=1723083184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015140/extras/60ee0dc55af0b898ac807695e2440f3b.mp4?t=1723083184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度探索:</h2>冒险进入地下王国的最深处，发现隐藏的宝藏和稀有矿物。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作系统:</h2>开采有价值的资源以制造和升级装备，提高您的生存能力并征服更艰难的挑战。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性的敌人:</h2>面对各种强大的敌人，包括蜘蛛、石像、蠕虫和幽灵，每个敌人都有独特的优点和缺点。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄之旅:</h2>踏上成为黑暗洞穴传说的英雄之旅，掌握地牢挖掘和寻宝的艺术。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
